===Formatting===
You can add your own commands to the Edit->Format menu.  See [Macros].
The default set is:
|| *OSX* || *Windows/Linux* || *Action* ||
||CMD-B||CTRL-B||Bold||
||CMD-I||CTRL-I||Italics||
||CMD-U||CTRL-U||Underline||
||ALT-SHIFT-C||||Text Color||
||ALT-CMD-P||ALT-CTRL-P||Paragraph||
||CMD-K||CTRL-K||Link||

===Ingredient List===
The Ingredient List in the Editor has some of it's own keyboard shortcuts.
These are important, because they are the only method of accessing these functions.

||SHIFT-UP||Move the selected row up||
||SHIFT-DOWN||Move the selected row down||
||SHIFT-DELETE||Clears the row||
||ALT-SHIFT-DELETE||Clears the entire table||
